<!-- Block 1: Hero Jumbotron -->
<div class="jumbotron text-white nri-custom-hero text-center break-large" style="background: #3687bd url('https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/cattle-and-rancher-in-pasture.jpg') no-repeat left bottom / cover;">
<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12">
<h1 class="h2"><strong>Regenerative ranching is about healthy soils and a stronger bottom line.</strong></h1>
<p class="lead"><strong>Applying regenerative agriculture principles allows farmers and ranchers in grazing animal production to be profitable and good stewards of the land.</strong></p>
<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary text-uppercase" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/subscribe/">Subscribe to our FREE regenerative email newsletter</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></div><div>
<!-- Block 2: Power of a Regenerative Mindset -->
    
<div class="container"> 
<div class="row break-small">
<div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
<h2><strong>The Power of a Regenerative Mindset</strong></h2>
    <p class="lead">Regenerative ranchers draw energy from their desire to improve the land and other productive attitudes.</p>
    </div></div>
<div class="row break-medium">
<div class="col-sm-4 text-center">
<p class="wysiwyg img text-primary"><img class="break-none img-circle" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/legacy/2021-winter/the-power-of-a-regenerative-mindset/the-burroughs-family.jpg" border="0" alt="Rosie Burroughs and her family"/></p>
<p class="lead break-none"><strong>Rosie Burroughs</strong></p>
<p>&ldquo;Take the time to be an observer, to look at what you&rsquo;re doing, and to know if what you&rsquo;re doing is working. It&rsquo;s good to be open-minded and willing to try.&rdquo;</p></div>
<div class="col-sm-4 text-center">
<p class="wysiwyg img text-primary"><img class="break-none img-circle" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/legacy/2021-winter/the-power-of-a-regenerative-mindset/jake-miller-and-family.jpg" border="0" alt="Jake Miller and his family"/></p>
<p class="lead break-none"><strong>Jake Miller</strong></p>
<p>&ldquo;The successful people I have seen [are the ones who] take time to monitor the range and see what&rsquo;s out there in terms of plant health and range conditions.&rdquo;</p>
</div>
<div class="col-sm-4 text-center">
<p class="wysiwyg img text-primary"><img class="break-none img-circle" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/legacy/2021-winter/the-power-of-a-regenerative-mindset/gail-fuller-and-lynette-miller.jpg" border="0" alt="Gail Fuller and his partner, Lynnette Miller"/></p>
<p class="lead break-none"><strong>Gail Fuller</strong></p>
<p>&ldquo;I knew I needed to make changes so future generations could have the same chance to do what I&rsquo;m doing.&rdquo;</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row break-large">
<div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg text-uppercase" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/legacy/the-power-of-a-regenerative-mindset/">Read more about the power of the regenerative mindset</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div></div><div>
<!-- Block 3: What is Regenerative Ranching? -->
<div class="jumbotron bg-primary break-none" style="box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2000px rgba(0,0,0,.35); background-color: #222; background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)), url('https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/aerial-view-of-pastures-and-road.jpg') no-repeat left bottom / cover;">  
<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="youtube" data-embed="37BCDKqUSVE"><button class="btn play-button text-primary" type="button"><span class="sr-only">Play</span></button></div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<h2 class="h3"><strong>What is regenerative ranching?</strong></h2>
<p class="lead"><strong><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/news/publications/ag-news-and-views/2020/march/regenerative-agriculture-is-about-direction-over-perfection/">Regenerative ranching</a></strong> is the process of restoring degraded grazing lands using practices based on ecological principles.</p>
<h2 class="h5"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/regenerative-agriculture/organic-vs-regenerative-agriculture/"><strong><u>How do organic agriculture and regenerative agriculture differ?</u></strong></a></h2>
<p>While buying organic food can assure you that the land on which it was grown was managed without the use of most synthetic fertilizers and pesticides, the label itself cannot tell you whether the health of the land is improving. Regenerative agriculture focuses on building soil health and restoring degraded land within a food production system.</p>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary text-uppercase" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/regenerative-agriculture">Learn more about <br class="hidden-lg"/> Regenerative Agriculture</a></p>
</div>  
</div>
</div>
</div> </div><div>
<!-- Block 4: Hand Holding Up Soil Image -->
    
<div class="jumbotron text-white break-none convertible-bg-parent" style="background: #191b1f;">
    <img alt="Noble consultant holding up a clump of healthy soil over a pasture." class="img-responsive convertible-bg break-small" style="object-position: 75% 25%;" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/hand-holding-soil.jpg"/>
     <div class="container">        
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                <h2 class="h3"><strong>Regenerative agriculture is the key to improving farmland and soil.</strong></h2>
                <p style="font-weight: 700;">Regenerative agriculture and regenerative ranching are <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/news/publications/legacy/2020/spring/the-journey/">reshaping how we think about farming and food production.</a></p>

                <p style="font-weight: 700;">Traditional ways of approaching agriculture and livestock production often rely on an overuse of chemical inputs and tillage. This can degrade the land and our environment while also undermining the producer&rsquo;s profitability.</p>

                <p style="font-weight: 700;">Regenerative agriculture is the process of <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/news/publications/ag-news-and-views/2019/march/5-reasons-why-soil-biology-matters-on-the-farm/">restoring degraded soils</a> using farming and grazing practices based on ecological principles. The benefits of regenerative agriculture practices include:</p>

                <ul style="font-weight: 700;">
                  <li>Increasing biodiversity in soil</li>
                    <li>Capturing carbon in the soils to combat climate variability</li>
                    <li>Improving water-holding capacity of soil, making it more drought- and flood- resilient</li>
                    <li>Decreasing the use of chemical inputs and subsequent pollution</li>
                    <li>Enhancing wildlife habitat</li>
                </ul>
                </div> 
                <div class="col-sm-6"></div>    
            </div> 
        </div> 
</div></div><div>
<!-- Block 5: Testimonial Videos -->    
    
<div class="jumbotron bg-primary break-large" style="background-color: #222; background: linear-gradient(90deg,  rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65),  rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65)),url('https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/cattle-in-sunny-pasture.jpg') no-repeat center / cover;">  
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 break-none">
                    <h2 class="text-center"><strong>Healthy Soil Provided These Ranchers a Solid Foundation.</strong></h2>
                              <div class="wysiwyg clearfix none"><p class="lead text-center">See how three ranching families overcame challenges to build profits and healthy soil.</p></div>

                </div>
                <div class="c-vid-mosaic break-large">
                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            <div class="clearfix"></div>  <!-- For some reaseon this needs to be here otherwise the first embed responsive disappears on small screens -->


    
                         <div class="youtube" data-embed="jkozZ2xq-8A">
        <button type="button" class="btn play-button text-primary"><span class="sr-only">Play</span></button>
        <img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://img.youtube.com/vi/jkozZ2xq-8A/sddefault.jpg" alt="Click here to play video.">
    <img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://img.youtube.com/vi/jkozZ2xq-8A/sddefault.jpg" alt="Click here to play video."></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-4">

<div class="youtube" data-embed="MCrU3tu-SLM">
