            <div class="col-xs-12 break-none text-center">
                <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary text-uppercase" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/annual-report/2020/resilient-how-healthy-soil-provides-ranchers-a-secure-foundation/">Read their stories here <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i></a>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div></div><div>
<!-- Block 6: Regenerative Ranching -->
    
<div class="container"> 
<div class="row break-small">
<div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
<h3 class="h2"><strong>Regenerative ranching begins with an understanding of how ecosystems work.</strong></h3>
<p class="lead">Regenerative ranchers commonly lower their input costs and develop skills in profitably managing their livestock and forages to feed the soil.</p>
    </div></div>
<div class="row break-large">
<div class="col-sm-4">
<img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/cattle-in-tall-grass.jpg" class="img-responsive break-small" alt="Cattle grazing in a tall-grass pasture.">
<h3 class="h5 text-uppercase text-green"><strong>Regenerative Ranching Focuses on the Land</strong></h3>
<p>Regenerative ranching focuses on enhancing and restoring the land, making it more resilient and supporting the health of the overall ecosystem.</p>
</div>   
<div class="col-sm-4 nri-home-col-center-border">
<img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/healthy-soil-clump.jpg" class="img-responsive break-small" alt="Noble Consultant holding up a clump of healthy soil.">
<h3 class="h5 text-uppercase text-green"><strong>Healthy Soils Benefit Society as a Whole</strong></h3>
<p>Healthy soils and ecosystems produce a variety of ecosystem services enjoyed by all of society, including carbon sequestration and water retention and filtration.</p>
</div>   
<div class="col-sm-4">
<img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/jeff-goodwin.jpg" class="img-responsive break-small" alt="Noble consultant, Jeff Goodwin, speaks with a group of ranchers.">
<h3 class="h5 text-uppercase text-green"><strong>Regenerative Ranching Is Good For Ranchers</strong></h3>
<p>Regenerative ranching is generally associated with holistic management and decision-making as well as managed grazing. Intentional management is good for ranchers.</p>
</div>   
</div>
</div>  </div><div>
<!-- Block 7: Regenerating The Land While Increasing Profitability -->
 
    
<div class="jumbotron text-white break-none" style="box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2000px rgba(0,0,0,.35); background-color: #222; background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)), url('https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/aerial-view-of-pastures-and-road.jpg') no-repeat left bottom / cover;">
<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12">
<h2><strong>Regenerating The Land While Increasing Ranchers&rsquo; Profitability is Noble's Goal</strong></h2>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-4"><img class="img-responsive break-small" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504im_/https://www.noble.org/globalassets/images/home/inspecting-the-soil.jpg" border="0" alt="Noble consultant, Jim Johnson, inspects a clump of soil with a rancher."/></div>
<div class="col-md-8">
<p class="lead">For more than 75 years, Noble Research Institute has built deep relationships with agricultural producers. This year, Noble is taking the next steps in the Institute&rsquo;s journey.</p>
<p class="lead">As we&rsquo;ve announced in recent months, we are focusing all of our operations on regenerative ranching that balances profitability and stewardship. Why? <strong>Because farmers and ranchers shouldn&rsquo;t have to choose one objective over the other.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/regenerative-agriculture/inviting-you-into-the-regenerative-journey/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg text-uppercase">Read More About <br class="hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg"/>Our Regenerative Journey</a></p>
<p><a class="btn text-uppercase" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220307201504/https://www.noble.org/message-to-ranchers/">Pausing Our Consultation Efforts. Read More Here.</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></div>

</main>
        
